Package builder.constraints.parameters

Class ParametersSumRelaxed

  • java.lang.Object
    • builder.constraints.parameters.ConstraintParameters
      • builder.constraints.parameters.ParametersSumRelaxed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Allocable, Freeable
    public class ParametersSumRelaxed
extends ConstraintParameters
    ParametersSumRelaxed
    Parameters of the relaxed Sum constraint.
    Here, the value of the label is not the label itself : we get the value of the label from a map.
    Contains the set of constrained variables, the bounds of the sum and the map associating labels with values.
